item.title: 'Undefined Symbol: PySlice_Unpack' error in Pytorch
item.description: Problem: ‘Undefined Symbol: PySlice_Unpack’ Environment: Pytorch = 1.0.1 Python = 3.6.0 Solution: Upgrade Python to 3.6.3. Seems like this is the only solution. Update by conda install python==3.6.3 command if using Miniconda in CLI.
